headline: 3 Hotels & Motels Stocks to Keep an Eye on Despite Industry Woes
summary: The industry faces challenges from rising costs and reduced travel from lower-income consumers. However, stocks like MAR, HLT and H will likely benefit from expansion efforts and other growth initiatives.
